page.content: {ALPINE, PHLOX, IRIS}, Sedum, Sempervivum, Saxifraga, Geranium, Erodium, Potentialla - over 100 varieties, 45p. Dwarf conifers 60p. Chiddingly {LOWER DICKER} spacious modern semi-detached house. Full gas central heating, large garden. 37,750 pounds. {ESCORT ESTATE 1300 GL} 1977, tax, M.O.T. well above average condition. 1,350 pounds. Golden Cross. {STRIPPED PINE KITCHEN} table with drawer,4'6" by 3' - 48 pounds. {FAMILY OF GNOMES} cannot be split. Cheap to feed. 30 pounds the lot. Tel - Camberlot Hall.
